observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the LDRRMO:
conduct a thorough review of all LDRRM funded programs and projects, including those under continuing appropriations, to assess their current status and progress;
coordinate with the concerned implementing offices/department identified in the LDRRMFIP to undertake steps in order to optimally utilize the DRRM Fund, such as monitoring the implementation of the PPAs to ensure that they are implemented within the target dates of completion, and in order to fully implement the PPAs prioritized and included in the LDRRMIP in support of disaster risk reduction and management activities, towards a more disaster resilient community.
